damn was htis packed full of great, lore building critters! from the drow to the githyanki! 
plus it had real cool art. the 1st ed Monster Manual had some iffy art, but the Fiend Folio had some real good ones, like the great &quot;warrior with 2 hand sword against lizard king&quot; 
 
 
