					<div id="post_message_1622674">
						<blockquote class="postcontent restore ">
							I have a book from 2001. No idea why I bought it, as I hadn't played since 84 or 85 at that point. Anyway -- its called &quot;Dungeons --  A Guide to Survival in the Realms Below&quot;.<br />
<br />
It basically covers several variant dungeon types, why they are built, what happens to them over the years, and so on. It also has a terrific section on building traps which never fails to make me giggle.<br />
<br />
Sorry -- I don't have much else at this point. Just started playing again about a month ago.<br />
<br />
Obligatory shout out to Grindel, who sent me the 3 books I do own!
						</blockquote>
