No kids ot pass it onto...kind of sucks that does.<br />
<br />
Gave away my Greyhawk stuff to a pal who's a huge fan of the setting (like the 1980 &quot;folio&quot; campaign setting) but his wife doesn't seem to like us gamers and has put the hems on him <img src="images/smilies/rolleyes.gif" border="0" alt="" title="Roll Eyes (Sarcastic)" class="inlineimg" /><br />
<br />
I had found, a long while back, a place that sold second hand D&amp;D stuff along with new, so I picked up amazing stuff dirt cheap. Hehe <img src="images/smilies/wink.gif" border="0" alt="" title="Wink" class="inlineimg" /><br />
<br />
Really wanted to GIVE my stuff to another D&amp;D fan but too heavy to post it all. Weighs a freaking ton.<br />
<br />
dumping last 50 or so Dragon/dungeon magazines at local charity shop when I'm feelling better (keeping lots of good ones, anything with Spelljammer/Dark Sun and specials, of course)<br />
Ah, for a TARDIS!
