				<h2 class="title icon icon0">
					Re: Fave items/books from D&amp;D? :)
				</h2>
				

						
						
				<div class="content">
					<div id="post_message_1623024">
						<blockquote class="postcontent restore ">
							My favorite D&amp;D item was the giant box set of a single massive underground dungeon - a map that spread out to be like 12'x12', and a giant thick manual going through the entire place.<br />
<br />
Sadly, I cannot remember the name of it. I have no doubt someone will cough it up before I can find it online.<br />
<br />
While I learned on 2nd Ed., and memorized all 3 source books front-to-back, I still think 1st Ed. has more flavor, even if it is less politically correct (e.g. different stat bonuses for males and females).
						</blockquote>
					</div>

					
				</div>
			</div>
			
